title: The Simpsons: Tapped Out v4.20.5 [Mod Cash/Donut]
description:

WHAT'S NEW

Springfield is heading west! (Or maybe it already was west? Weâ€™re still not really sure on its location.) With dirt roads, old timey buildings, bandits, and a treasure trove of gold, youâ€™ll be dying of dysentery before you can shoot a buffalo.
Play today to:
